>立足中国科学院丰富的科学资源，面向公众提供前沿科学解读、精彩科普视频以及趣味科教服务。<br>知乎机构号：<a href="https://www.zhihu.com/org/zhong-guo-ke-pu-bo-lan" data-editable="true" data-title="中国科普博览 - 知乎">中国科普博览 - 知乎</a><br>微信 ID：kepubolan</p></div></li></ul></div></div><div class="module guests"><div class="module-header"><h3>嘉宾</h3></div><div class="module-body"><ul class="items"><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/li-miao-7" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$li-miao-7'><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/37411037359278e65eba66c9a74a411d_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="李淼"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/nobel2018/li-miao-7/answers" class="answers text-muted">2 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/li-miao-7" data-hovercard='p$t$li-miao-7'>李淼</a><span class="icon icon-badge-identity icon-badge" data-tooltip="s$b$已认证的个人"></span><div class="bio">理论物理以及诗歌</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/fuwocheng" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$fuwocheng'><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/c096f565bad088a2b709d460f066e1dc_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="傅渥成"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/nobel2018/fuwocheng/answers" class="answers text-muted">2 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/fuwocheng" data-hovercard='p$t$fuwocheng'>傅渥成</a><span class="icon icon-badge-id-an icon-badge" data-tooltip="s$b$优秀回答者 · 已认证的个人"></span><div class="bio">东京大学 <span class="bull">&bull;</span> 博士后</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/sijichun" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$sijichun'><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-8906a56d80b98224eb1d544c9dc69c74_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="慧航"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/nobel2018/sijichun/answers" class="answers text-muted">4 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/sijichun" data-hovercard='p$t$sijichun'>慧航</a><span class="icon icon-badge-id-an ico